name: Danny Niblett
text: They helped this ol dude get what he needed and didn't even fuss. I thanked them for being so patient with me. I had to pick up a birth certificate for my mom. Some of the questions had me puzzled but they got me straight. Thanks again

name: Patti Griffith
text: They were very nice and helpful. Sent us to the correct place.

name: Ashley Eager
text: The vital records staff was very polite and quick!

name: Julia Cornelius
text: I love our health department the people are nice and they make u understand if u dont

name: Aimee Payne
text: Scheduled a health screening appointment for work at 9:00am.  Arrived prior to 9:00am.  At 9:20 someone else came in for the  same type of appointment, hers was scheduled at 9:30.  They called her back first, within 5 minutes, because "they could not remember who was next."  At 9:55am I left.  This is ridiculous. Why take appointments if you are called back based on the staff's memory? Total incompetence.

name: Justin Archer
text: They are always short and give you the run around!
